    <title>Activities</title>

  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>
      Activities
    </h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Compute the angular velocity of each rod when its angle with the 
        horizontal is 0 &#8804;<i> &#966;</i> &#8804; <b>phi</b> &lt; &#960;/2. Which 
        rod will fall faster?
      </li>
      <li>
        Press <b>Start</b> to check your guess.
      </li>
      <li>
        Which is the geometrical form of the trajectories of the center point 
        and upper end of the right rod?
      </li>
      <li>
        Check <b>Trajectories</b> and run again the simulation to check your 
        guess.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </body>
